《'''名聲大噪'''》（{{lang-en|''Smash''}}，又譯：'''一鳴驚人'''），是一部[[美國|美國]][[音樂劇|音樂]][[連續劇|連續劇]]，由[[特蕾莎·雷貝克|特蕾莎·雷貝克]]（{{link-en|Theresa Rebeck|Theresa Rebeck}}）創作，[[史提芬·史匹堡|史提芬·史匹堡]]（Steven Spielberg）有份協助製作。 

這部劇集於2012年2月6日在美國[[NBC|NBC]]電視台首播，由[[夢工場電視|夢工場電視]]（DreamWorks Television）製作。<ref name=PremiereDate>{{cite web|last=Seidman|first=Robert|title=It's Official: NBC Premieres Second Season of 'The Voice' After Super Bowl; 'Smash' Premieres Next Day|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/08/01/its-official-nbc-premieres-second-season-of-the-voice-after-super-bowl-smash-premieres-next-day/99337/|work=TV by the Numbers|date=August 1, 2011|accessdate=August 1, 2011|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091318/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/08/01/its-official-nbc-premieres-second-season-of-the-voice-after-super-bowl-smash-premieres-next-day/99337/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=bcc051111>{{cite news | url = http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/468158-NBC_Orders_Pilots_Smash_Whitney_More.php | title = NBC Orders Pilots ‘Smash,' ‘Whitney,' More | last = Morabito | first = Andrea | date = May 11, 2011 | work = ''Broadcasting & Cable'' | accessdate = June 10, 2011 | archive-date = 2011-05-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110518214852/http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/468158-NBC_Orders_Pilots_Smash_Whitney_More.php | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=nbcups>{{cite news | url = http://www.deadline.com/2011/05/nbc-unveils-2011-12-primetime-schedule/ | title = NBC Unveils 2011-2012 Primetime Schedule | last = Andreeva | first = Nellie | date = May 15, 2011 | work = [[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] | accessdate = June 10, 2011 | archive-date = 2013-10-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131013200517/http://www.deadline.com/2011/05/nbc-unveils-2011-12-primetime-schedule/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

