==製作==
===構思===
[[File:Debra_Messing_at_the_2009_Tribeca_Film_Festival_3.jpg|left]]（Debra Messing），《名聲大噪》的主演之一，曾是NBC情景喜劇《[[威爾與格蕾絲|威爾與格蕾絲]]》（''Will & Grace''）的女主角。]]
《名聲大噪》的製作自2009年便開始。原本史提芬·史匹堡構思了這部劇集的概念，並為此進行了多年工作，其後當時[[Showtime|Showtime]]電視台的娛樂主管[[羅伯特·格林布拉特|羅伯特·格林布拉特]]（{{link-en|Robert Greenblatt|Robert Greenblatt}}）與史匹堡合作開始發展這部劇集。<ref name=showspielteam>{{cite news | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118008994?refCatId=14 | title = Showtime, Spielberg team on series | last = Littleton | first = Cynthia | date = September 22, 2009 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | accessdate = June 10, 2011 | archive-date = 2012-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121108074210/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118008994?refCatId=14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>原本構思是想每季都圍繞一部新的音樂劇，而且如果這些「音樂劇」值得登上舞台，史匹堡更考慮會將它放在真正的[[百老匯|百老匯]]舞台上演出。<ref name="concept">{{cite web |last=Green |first=Jesse |url=http://nymag.com/arts/tv/features/smash-2012-1/index1.html |title=Will 'Smash' on NBC Be a Success? - New York Magazine |publisher=''[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]'' |date=January 2, 2012 |accessdate=January 16, 2012 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812040130/https://nymag.com/arts/tv/features/smash-2012-1/index1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>這部節目的靈感來源主要是NBC的經典政治劇《[[白宮群英|白宮群英]]》（''The West Wing''）和英國[[ITV|ITV]]的經典時代劇《[[樓上樓下|樓上樓下]]》（''Upstairs, Downstairs''）。<ref name="concept"/>格林布拉特於2011年1月過檔到NBC後將這部節目也帶過去，並由特蕾莎·雷貝克負責創作《名聲大噪》和撰寫首播集劇本，<ref name="concept"/>而雷貝克是由執行製作[[克雷格·薩坦|克雷格·薩坦]]（Craig Zadan）與[[尼爾·邁倫|尼爾·邁倫]]（Neil Meron）推薦給史匹堡和格林布拉特。<ref name="concept"/>NBC在2011年1月預訂製作《名聲大噪》的試播集，並在2011至2012年度電視季度上的推出這部節目。<ref name=pilotordered>{{cite news | url = http://www.deadline.com/2011/01/nbc-picks-up-2-pilots-including-hourlong-musical-from-steven-spielberg/ | title = NBC Orders Steven Spielberg Musical Pilot | last = Andreeva | first = Nellie | date = January 21, 2011 | work = [[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] | accessdate = June 10, 2011 | archive-date = 2013-10-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131013180851/http://www.deadline.com/2011/01/nbc-picks-up-2-pilots-including-hourlong-musical-from-steven-spielberg/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 

[[米高爾·梅耶|米高爾·梅耶]]（{{link-en|Michael Mayer (director)|Michael Mayer (director)|Michael Mayer}}）執導了首播集，史匹堡並擔任了執行製作之一。<ref name=nbcups/>單單首播集就耗費了NBC約750萬美元生產。<ref name="concept"/><ref name=pilotcost>{{cite news | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/heard-inside-upfront-parties-presentations-190389 | title = Heard Inside the Upfront Parties and Presentations | last = Masters | first = Kim | last2 = Guthries | first2 = Marisa | date = May 20, 2011 | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | accessdate = June 10, 2011 | archive-date = 2018-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181116032135/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/heard-inside-upfront-parties-presentations-190389 | dead-url = no }}</ref>在2011年5月11日，NBC正式計劃投入將這構思發展為劇集。當四天後NBC電視網公佈他們在2011至2012年度的節目表時，這部節目的首播被置於季中時段播出。<ref name=nbcups/>NBC選擇將這部節目留到季中播映是因為要將它與[[真人秀|真人秀]]《[[美國之聲|美國之聲]]》（''The Voice''）配搭一起在週一晚上推出。<ref name=pairing>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/17/business/media/17adco.html?_r=1 | title = For Fox and NBC, Let the Singing Begin | last = Carter | first = Bill | last2=Stelter | first2= Brian |date = May 16, 2011 | work = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | accessdate = June 10, 2011 }}</ref>同年8月1日，NBC公佈《名聲大噪》將定於翌年2月6日首播，是[[超級碗|超級碗]]後的首晚，同時亦在冬季初作出大量《名聲大噪》的推廣來配合。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/153252-Smash-Drama-Series-Will-Launch-in-February-2012-With-Christian-Borle-Megan-Hilty-Debra-Messing |title="Smash" Drama Series Will Launch in February 2012 With Christian Borle, Megan Hilty, Debra Messing |accessdate=2012-03-03 |archive-date=2012-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111061728/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/153252-Smash-Drama-Series-Will-Launch-in-February-2012-With-Christian-Borle-Megan-Hilty-Debra-Messing |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/08/01/voice-premiere-date/ |title=NBC announces 'The Voice' return date |accessdate=2012-03-03 |archive-date=2013-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530051305/http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/08/01/voice-premiere-date/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在NBC的節目巡禮裡，官方宣佈《名聲大噪》將有15集，以配合《美國之聲》的播放。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hitfix.com/blogs/whats-alan-watching/posts/press-tour-nbc-boss-on-community-parks-and-recreation-chuck-and-more|title=Press tour: NBC boss on 'Community,' 'Parks and Recreation,' 'Chuck' and more|first=Alan|last=Sepinwall|work=HitFix|publisher=HitFix.com|date=August 1, 2011|accessdate=January 15, 2012|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210415/http://www.hitfix.com/blogs/whats-alan-watching/posts/press-tour-nbc-boss-on-community-parks-and-recreation-chuck-and-more|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===劇組人員===
《名聲大噪》是[[環球電視|環球電視]]（Universal Television）與[[夢工場|夢工場]]（DreamWorks）。<ref name=nbcups/>特蕾莎雷貝克是此劇的創作人，並寫了試播集的劇本。<ref name=nbcups/>此劇亦有數目很多的[[執行製作|執行製作]]，包括史蒂芬·史匹堡、克雷格·薩坦、尼爾·邁倫、雷貝克、戴洛爾·法蘭克（Darryl Frank）、賈斯汀·法爾維（Justin Falvey）。<ref name=nbcups/>馬克·沙文和斯科特·威德曼也是執行製作，同時兼任作曲家。<ref name=nbcups/>

