== 收視率 ==
《名聲大噪》的首播集奪得了1144萬觀眾，並在18-49歲觀眾收視率獲得3.8/10的佳績，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/07/tv-ratings-monday-nbc-has-a-big-voice-the-day-after-super-bowl-cbs-down-not-out-castle-sees-lows-big-drops-for-house-alcatraz/118898/ |title=TV Ratings Monday: NBC Has a Big Voice the Day After Super Bowl; CBS Down, Not Out; 'Castle' Sees Lows; Big Drops for 'House,' 'Alcatraz' |accessdate=2012-03-03 |archive-date=2012-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302122227/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/07/tv-ratings-monday-nbc-has-a-big-voice-the-day-after-super-bowl-cbs-down-not-out-castle-sees-lows-big-drops-for-house-alcatraz/118898/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/07/monday-final-ratings-the-voice-alcatraz-house-two-and-a-half-men-adjusted-up/119033/ |title=Monday Final Ratings: 'The Voice,' 'Alcatraz,' 'House,' 'Two and a Half Men' Adjusted Up |accessdate=2012-03-03 |archive-date=2012-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209211614/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/07/monday-final-ratings-the-voice-alcatraz-house-two-and-a-half-men-adjusted-up/119033/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>也是2011至2012年度電視季度第三高首播集收視率的新劇，排名僅次於《[[童話鎮|童話鎮]]》（''Once Upon a Time ''）及《[[觸摸未來|觸摸未來]]》（''Touch''）之後。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tv-ratings-smash-voice-super-bowl-287606 |title=TV Ratings: 'Smash' Sings for NBC, 'The Voice' Stays Strong After Super Bowl |accessdate=2012-03-03 |archive-date=2018-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615083141/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tv-ratings-smash-voice-super-bowl-287606 |dead-url=no }}</ref>《名聲大噪》首播集也成為了該年度10時檔期節目收視最高之節目，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2012/02/07/smash-ratings/ |title='Smash' starts solid; 'Voice' tops Monday ratings |accessdate=2012-03-03 |archive-date=2014-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210161049/http://insidetv.ew.com/2012/02/07/smash-ratings/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>也是NBC自2008年11月以來在該檔期奪得最高的收視率和觀眾人數。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://playbill.com/news/article/159427-Smash-Ratings-Are-Solid-Musical-TV-Series-Off-to-a-Promising-Start |title="Smash" Ratings Are Solid; Musical TV Series Off to a Promising Start |accessdate=2012-03-03 |archive-date=2012-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209214345/http://playbill.com/news/article/159427-Smash-Ratings-Are-Solid-Musical-TV-Series-Off-to-a-Promising-Start |dead-url=no }}</ref>可是之後幾集《名聲大噪》的收視率不斷下降，至2月27日播出的第四集只剩下了660萬觀眾和2.3/6的收視率。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/28/monday-final-ratings-2-broke-girls-adjusted-up-smash-castle-adjusted-down-daytona-500-final-ratings/122198/ |title=Monday Final Ratings: '2 Broke Girls' Adjusted Up; 'Smash,' 'Castle' Adjusted Down + 'Daytona 500' Final Ratings |accessdate=2012-03-03 |archive-date=2012-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301172834/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/28/monday-final-ratings-2-broke-girls-adjusted-up-smash-castle-adjusted-down-daytona-500-final-ratings/122198/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

